# Drizzle

[[!img drizzle-logo.png alt="Drizzle logo" class="projectlogo" link="no"]]

Drizzle is a database server originally forked from MySQL code base.
Drizzle's focus is on mimimization, reducing the core to a microkernel,
and heavily embracing plugins for extensibility.

### Project Liaison

Monty Taylor

### Services

* Accepting donations and holding funds
* Paying for project expenses
* Holding intangible assets
* Accounting and auditing
